data.title: Minneapolis StarTribune
data.meta_description: Minneapolis StarTribune - a place for remembering loved ones; a space for sharing memories, life stories, milestones, to express condolences, and celebrate life of your loved ones
data.text:
Christopher Elliott

Christopher Arlen Elliott, 66, passed away on June 13, 2024 surrounded by his children and their partners.

Arthur Launer

Launer, Arthur Age 80, passed away peacefully on Aug. 24th, 2024. Art was born in Milwaukee, WI on Oct. 28th, 1943, growing up in Menomonee Falls. He worked for Northwest Airlines retiring in 2005. Marilou Thibault

Thibault, Marilou Elaine 81, passed away 8/26/24. Per her instructions, no services are planned. Complete obituary to be in Sunday 9/1/24 newspaper.

Bernard Gaytko

Gaytko, Bernard "Bernie" M., Sr. Age 88, of Chanhassen, departed this life for his Heavenly adventure on August 14, 2024. Preceded in death by parents Michael and Anna Gaytko of Youngstown, Ohio.
